Description: GDG New Delhi is proud to present DevFest 2023, the biggest event of the year for developers, designers, and techies. This one-day festival will feature multiple tracks of tech sessions, communities, and projects, as well as food and fun activities. Whether you're a seasoned pro or just getting started in the tech world, DevFest has something for everyone. So mark your calendars, wear a big smile and we'll see you there!

DevFest Mangalore 2023 will be the largest technical event and the first ever GDG festival in Mangalore as we set to host 1000+ developers from various geographies including Mangalore, Udupi and Kasargod.
GDG DevFest Ahmedabad brings together the world class experts in Android, Web and Cloud technologies to Ahmedabad for sessions, workshops and showcases.

Venue: Seminar Hall, Laxmi Narayan Dubey College, Motihari
Description: Join us for DevFests Motihari. DevFests are local conferences hosted by Google Developer Groups (GDG) around the world. Each DevFest is crafted by its local organizers to fit the needs and interests of its local developer community. Whether it be through hands-on learning experiences, technical talks delivered in local languages by experts, or by simply meeting fellow local developers, DevFest attendees learn how to build together and innovate on Google's developer tools.
